                <note rend="inline" type="source">711.4215 Air Pollution/498: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Minister in Canada</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Robbins</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1934-04-21T16:00:00-05:00"
                            >April 21, 1934—4 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>40. Your No. 38, April 20, 6 p.m. Department deems it important that note
                    embodying Nos. 300 and 303 be presented. Department has given assurance this
                    would be done.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Phillips</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
